How to configure OpenTx to access telemetry data
Redundancy Bus - Manuel utilisateur - vPlus.En1 - P03
On a FrSky radio with firmware version 2.2 and higher:
1- Turn on the transmitter and select the "TELEMETRY" menu of your current model;
2- In the "TELEMETRY" page, go down and select "Discover new sensors";
3- The illustration below shows the newly discovered sensors from the .
Note : • The number assigned to each sensor may differ depending on the equipment of your model.
• The illustration only shows the sensors from the .

tspan.tspan: • Sensors from the receiver(s) or other equipment are not voluntarily shown in the illustration.

text.tspan: 5- You can now configure what telemetry displays 1-4 should display.
